    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "We're listing this vehicle honestly as a car in poor condition, and we want any potential buyer to have a completely accurate picture before reaching out. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 there are multiple deep scratches, dents, and areas of rust visible on the body panels, and the paint has faded and peeled in several spots. The interior is similarly worn, with torn upholstery, cracked dashboard trim, and a strong musty odor that will require professional attention. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues \u2014 it starts and can be driven, but it runs rough, and there are warning lights active on the dashboard that have not been diagnosed or repaired. The tires are worn unevenly and will need replacement soon. This car is best suited for a buyer comfortable with a significant repair project or someone looking for parts. We are pricing it accordingly and will not misrepresent its condition \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in good condition, and the asking price reflects that honestly \u2014 please read this full description before reaching out. The car is in solid, reliable shape with no major mechanical issues; it starts consistently, drives smoothly, and all primary systems (engine, transmission, brakes, and cooling) are functioning as expected. Cosmetically, the car shows normal signs of everyday use \u2014 you may notice minor surface scratches, small door dings, or light wear on interior surfaces such as the seat bolsters and steering wheel, but nothing that detracts significantly from its appearance or usability. The tires have good tread remaining, and routine maintenance has been kept up to date. This is a dependable, everyday driver that doesn't need immediate repairs, making it a practical choice for someone looking for solid transportation at a fair price. Buyers are welcome to arrange a pre-purchase inspection, which I fully encourage.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you consider making a purchase. The exterior shows its age \u2014 you'll notice several scratches, some paint fading, and minor dents in a few panels. It's not a showroom car, but the body is structurally sound. The interior has moderate wear consistent with regular use: expect worn seat fabric, some scuffs on the dashboard trim, and a few small stains. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it has some quirks \u2014 there may be minor issues that a competent mechanic could address without major expense. We recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting into. This is a practical, usable vehicle at a fair price, suited for a buyer who wants reliable transportation and doesn't mind putting a little work into it.",
